INSERT INTO `faqs_content` VALUES (11,'Does Spirit Offer Compensation for Canceled Flights?','<p>Yes, Spirit Airlines offer travelers their canceled flight ticket compensation, which always depends on the situation. For example, suppose your flight is delayed for Spirit. In that case, you are eligible for two options referred to as total compensation, you may also reschedule your booking, or else you can file a request for compensation, and you will get it accordingly.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-11-07','spirit-airlines-compensation'),(12,'Does Spirit Give You Credit for Cancelled Flights?','<p>Yes, at Spirit Airlines, customers who face the issues of canceled tickets directly from the airline are offered credit instead of refunds, and the credit will always be as per the previously booked itinerary. However, if you want to know the credit amount, directly consult it with the official representative of Spirit Airlines via 1-855-728-3555, and you will receive proper assistance.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-07-24','spirit-airlines-compensation'),(35,'How To Do Auto Check-in in SpiceJet?','<p>The best you can do about SpiceJet Airlines auto check-in is use the official site page and process it through just by entering the details of the ticket, like booking reference code/PNR number and last name of the passenger and retrieve your ticket online, and the auto check-in is preceded quite conveniently with SpiceJet Airlines.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-11','how-do-i-get-my-mobile-boarding-pass-from-spicejet'),(36,'How Soon Can I Web Check-in SpiceJet?','<p>If your concern is regarding how early I should get the check-in completed with SpiceJet Airlines, then it is always concerned with the basis of the rip type you have selected. In this situation, SpiceJet airline check-in is available within 48 hours from the scheduled departure. It will shut down 2 hours before the withdrawal; if you cannot process web or self-service KIOSK check-in, head straight to the helpdesk live representative. You will then be getting assistance direct from the assistant.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-11','how-do-i-get-my-mobile-boarding-pass-from-spicejet'),(37,'How To Process SpiceJet Web Check-in?','<p>Now to complete the web check-in, you are supposed to use the official website of SpiceJet Airlines; once you visit the official site page, you can choose the check-in tab and then after that, enter the check-in required details like PNR number or booking reference code along with passengers last name and ahead of this complete the check-in by mentioning necessary information.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-11','how-do-i-get-my-mobile-boarding-pass-from-spicejet'),(38,'How Do I Check in with SpiceJet?','<p>While you need to complete check-in with SpiceJet Airlines, then, there are several procedures available which are online and offline. As you try online check-in, the best you can do is by selecting the mobile application, or else you can do it by using the official website. On the other hand, offline ways to check in with SpiceJet Airlines are Self-service KIOSK or directly visiting the helpdesk of SpiceJet at the airport for instant approaches.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-11','how-do-i-get-my-mobile-boarding-pass-from-spicejet'),(47,'How Many Hawaiian Miles do You Need for a Free Ticket?','<p>When you wish to use Hawaiian Miles to reserve your flight ticket at no cost, you must have at least 7500 to 20000 miles for one way to travel within Hawaii. You can earn with this program, which can be used for award flights with partner airlines that you can choose to travel using Hawaiian Miles. Hence, if you have abundant miles, you can ingeniously plan your trip free to your desired destination at zero cost.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-21','how-do-i-transfer-hawaiianmiles'),(48,'How Much is 70000 Hawaiian Miles Worth?','<p>If you have accumulated around 70000 Hawaiian Miles, it is worth $630 that you can use to make a single purchase for a round trip to your destination within Hawaii. You also get the welcome bonus to purchase extra items during your flight journey, making your trip convenient. When you earn at least 70000 Hawaiian Miles, you will be able to use the world elite card welcome offer that you can use to book your flight ticket or purchase an extra seat for the main cabin significantly.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-21','how-do-i-transfer-hawaiianmiles'),(49,'How Much is 10000 Hawaiian Miles Worth?','<p>When you have 10000 Hawaiian Miles, it is worth about $120 and can be used to purchase your seat conveniently. You can select your preferred seat to reserve in Economy and Business class and make your flight journey suitable until you reach your required destination.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-21','how-do-i-transfer-hawaiianmiles'),(51,'How Do I Access My Hawaiian Miles?','<p>When you join Hawaiian Miles, you can check the miles and their credit details easily. Hence, if you wish to access your Hawaiian Miles and check the complete information for your miles, you must go through the steps below.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First, you need to log in to your Hawaiian Miles after accessing the official booing website of Hawaiian Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>You will access your account dashboard and locate the navigation bar on the left hand and check Hawaiian Miles, and click on the statement.</li>\r\n	<li>You can print your Hawaiian Miles statement if you need to get further details for your miles, especially.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-21','how-do-i-transfer-hawaiianmiles'),(57,'Can I Take American Airlines Flight Insurance for Domestic Flights?','<p>Yes, you can purchase American Airlines flight insurance for domestic flights. AA offers several number trip insurance plans through Allianz Global Assistance, a third-party insurance company. These plans can cover various risks, including trip cancellation, interruption, lost or delayed luggage, and medical expenses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can purchase American Airlines flight insurance when you book your flight or up to 24 hours after your ticket. Its cost will rely on the plan you choose and your circumstances.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-08-24','how-to-get-flight-insurance-american-airlines'),(58,'Can I Add Insurance to my flight after booking American?','<p>Yes, you can add insurance right after the booking on American Airlines. It is essential to check with suitable guidance for adding your insurance after a booking with American Airlines. You must contact a customer representative team to know the specific details to add your travel insurance to your booking. It can assist you in explaining your trip insurance benefits for your convenience suitably. You might get an offer with insurance coverage for flight-related issues such as trip cancellation, trip interruption, medical expenses, emergency evacuation, and baggage loss if the policy is purchased before a specific deadline of flight scheduled departure on American Airlines.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-02-08','how-to-get-flight-insurance-american-airlines'),(59,'Does American Airlines trip insurance cover flight changes?','<p>Yes, when you book your flight ticket with American Airlines, it is possible to change your flight ticket, and you don&rsquo;t need to pay any charges if you have added travel insurance. If your flight is cancelled due to severe weather or any technical faults with your flight, you can change your flight and re-book it for a further available flight date and avoid paying any extra charges accordingly.</p>\r\n','Active',NULL,NULL,'2023-02-08','how-to-get-flight-insurance-american-airlines');
