hen proceed with the process.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After that, you need to move to the add to apple wallet option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You can see a small window that will open where you are required to confirm by tapping on add tab.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, you can see your boarding pass will be added to your Apple wallet.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Do I Check-in Online for Malaysia Airlines?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>While making the reservation with Malaysia Airlines, the passenger needs to check in before boarding the flight as it is compulsory to check in because, after that, the passenger will get their boarding pass. If you are confused about the modes through which you can check-in. You can check in with Malaysia Airlines by using different methods. You need to go through the information given below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How Do I Check-in Online for Malaysia Airlines?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To check in with Malaysia Airlines, you can use the online process. It is one of the expeditious modes. To use this process, you need to follow the steps as per described below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Open the official web link of Malaysia Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>On the homepage of Malaysia Airlines, you will get the check-in option. Click on that.</li>\r\n	<li>Type your booking reference number and last name in the following sections. Tap on the check-in option.</li>\r\n	<li>You will get complete details of the flight on your screen. Select the ticket on which you want to check in. Tap on the continue option.</li>\r\n	<li>Once you complete all the steps, Malaysia Airlines will send you the confirmation message on your email or mobile phone.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>When can I check in online with Malaysia Airlines?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can make the online check-in 24 hours before the departure of the flight. The check-in time of Malaysia Airlines totally relies on the flight on which the passengers make the booking. To check the time, you need to go through the Malaysia Airline Check-in policy as per mentioned below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The passengers with the domestic flight need to check in at least 3 hours before the departure of the flight.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are traveling on an international flight, then you can check in 2 hours before the departure of the flight.</li>\r\n	<li>If the passenger adds accessibility assistance or any kind of assistance during the check-in, then you need to cancel the previous check-in and start the new check-in process.</li>\r\n	<li>If you add extra baggage during the check-in, then you need to start the next check-in after canceling the previous check-in.</li>\r\n	<li>You can use both an online and offline process to check in with Malaysia Airlines.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Can I Do a Web Check-in with Malaysia Airlines?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You can do Malaysia Airlines Web Check-in<strong> </strong>by using its application. You need to follow the directions as per mentioned below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First, download the Malaysia Airlines application on your devices.</li>\r\n	<li>Now enter your login credentials and tap on the continue option.</li>\r\n	<li>Tap on the Check-in option.</li>\r\n	<li>Enter the booking reference number and last name in the following sections. Tap on the check-in option.</li>\r\n	<li>You will get the details of the flight and make the selection as per your need.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Click on the continue option.</li>\r\n	<li>You will get the confirmation message for check-in on your email or mobile phone.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conclusion:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the help of the procedures as per mentioned above, you can check in at Malaysia Airlines. You can also make a Kiosk check in. You just need to enter your information into the machine that is available at the airport. You can check in at the airport 2 hours before the departure of the flight. For further assistance, you can also contact the customer service representative of Malaysia Airlines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','Find the here online process for how to get boarding pass Malaysia airlines and get check-in via mobile phone and also know how to add boarding pass on Google / Apple wallet.',NULL,'How To Get Boarding Pass Malaysia Airlines?','','Malaysia Airline Check in policy, Online Boarding Pass Malaysia Airlines, How do I add my Malaysia Airlines boarding pass ','Check-in','2023-07-28','Active','','','','How To Get Boarding Pass Malaysia Airlines | Web- Check-in / Mobile','how-to-get-boarding-pass-malaysia-airlines'),(20,NULL,'<h2><strong>Etihad Airways Boarding Pass and Online Check-in at Airport</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Suppose you seek Etihad Airways boarding pass information about check-in before the scheduled flight departure. Thus to learn the proper steps for getting your Etihad Airways boarding pass, you shall read the below-referred guidelines from here; appropriate assistance is guaranteed for your help.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Online Steps to Get a Boarding Pass at Etihad Airways:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First of all, you need to visit the official website of Etihad Airways.</li>\r\n	<li>Now at the site homepage, log in to your account and then straightaway tap over the check-in.</li>\r\n	<li>Within this page, enter the booking reference number alongside mentioning the traveler&#39;s last name.</li>\r\n	<li>Retrieve your ticket and ahead click on the check-in button.</li>\r\n	<li>Next, you have various options to complete, such as seat selection, baggage addition, or class change, which will be as per your preference.</li>\r\n	<li>Further, tap on confirm button, and you have completed all the procedures regarding Etihad Airways check-in.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, you can print or download your boarding pass over the official site page.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Etihad Airways Boarding Pass has Yet to be Received.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are instances, too, when most of the travelers face the general issues regarding not receiving the boarding pass, and if this is the case, then you should first acknowledge the common reasons as referred to below for proper guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>As the boarding pass is processed just after your online check-in, and if it is delayed, it might get stuck in the queue as last-minute check-in or boarding pass is quite familiar with travelers.</li>\r\n	<li>Or you may have entered the wrong credentials for generating the boarding pass page, and it may get delayed accordingly.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Thus, these are a few of the generic points you can consider for delaying or not receiving a boarding pass, and if you face the issue still, then contact Etihad Airways customer service representative because then you will get direct assistance from the expert.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Download the Boarding Pass at Etihad Airways:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you tried to download the boarding pass with the help of Etihad Airways online procedure but still need to complete the process, then in that scenario, the most appropriate action you can take is referred to below for your guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Self-Service KIOSK:&nbsp;</strong>You can access the airport&#39;s available self-service KIOSK machine to get a boarding pass. As with this machine option, access your official ticket onscreen. Then, tap on the download option (at the official email address) or get the print direct from the KIOSK machine.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>At airport helpdesk:&nbsp;</strong>Travellers can visit the helpdesk at the airport and provide the available window assistance, and you will then quickly receive service for getting your boarding pass direct from the assistant.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Contact Etihad Airways:</strong>&nbsp;Communication is always counted as one of the best mediums because you can receive immediate help over the call as it is direct from the available assistant. You need to provide the ticket details 