t the complete steps, then, below are the following that are mentioned in a proper way:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Open the authorized site of Qatar Airlines and then move to the help option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Now, access the contact us tab where you need to start searching for the live chat option, and when you get that then, click on it.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You will able to see a small chat box that opens up on your screen where you are able to send them all the queries and get the resolutions.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Long Does it Take for Qatar Airways to Reply?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Qatar Airways will take some time to give reply to all the complaints that they get, and if you need to know that, then here are all the details that are mentioned below:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are connected with them through the online method, then this will take a longer time to get a response from their side, and the timing is from 30 to 60 business days. The online methods include live chat, official email address, and social media handle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And if you get to connect with customer services through an official contact number, then you will get a response in a short time, or you will get a wait time to connect with real assistance.</p>\r\n','Get call away Qatar Airways customer service via phone number and talk to live representative to report your queries and customers can also connect with Whatsapp chat, email via sending a text message and they will reply to sms/email soon. ',NULL,'How Do I Make A Call to Qatar from my Cell Phone?','','How do I make a call to Qatar from my cell phone, ','article','2023-08-11','Active','','','','How Do I Make A Call to Qatar from my Cell Phone | Whatsapp | Agent','how-do-i-make-a-call-to-qatar-from-my-cell-phone'),(41,NULL,'<p>Qatar Airways is well-known for providing passengers with the best help and world-class flight services. They even ensure that their agent is available for them on a 24-hour basis. The passengers traveling on a long-haul flight need more assistance as it can be tiring to be seated in one place for 7 to 8 hours. On the one hand, the business and first-class users get incliner seats, and the passengers who booked a long flight in economy or economy classic have to bear with long seating hours. That is why Qatar Airways allow them to select the seat as per their preference and have a safe journey.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Qatar Seat Selection Policy</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The seat selection procedure is only available after you have booked your flight with Qatar Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>The airline will assign the seats; you must pay the selection fees to select your preferred seat.</li>\r\n	<li>The airline&#39;s frequent flyer programs are free of seat selection fees.</li>\r\n	<li>Seat selection is possible in the same class in which your airline ticket was purchased. Changing the class will be treated as a flight change, with various fees and procedures.</li>\r\n	<li>If you booked your ticket in business or first class, you do not have to pay the seat selection fees at the airport.</li>\r\n	<li>You can choose a seat on Qatar Airlines by using your miles, vouchers, or coupons.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Can I choose my seat on Qatar Economy Classic?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The airlines allow the passengers to proceed with the seat selection during reservation or by using the &#39;Manage Booking&#39; option. The steps that need to be followed to make the changes in your existing reservation are mentioned here for you as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visit the airline&#39;s official website and look for the &#39;Manage/Check-in option.&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>Once you get onto that box, enter your booking reference code along with the passenger&#39;s last name to click on the option of &quot;Manage Booking.&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Proceed to get redirected to the flight details page, and choose the seat selection option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A seat map of your flight class will appear on your screen, where you need to choose your preferred seat as per your preference.</li>\r\n	<li>No other change is allowed to be made during the seat selection process.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Once the selection is made and confirmed, they will redirect you to the payment page.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Follow the on-screen process to make the payment for your seat selection, and once it&#39;s done, the confirmation will get sent to your email.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Qatar Airways Seat Upgrade</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>People can also choose the auto-upgrade option and change their flight class preference even after the booking by upgrading their ticket from one class to another. The rules that are required to be known by them are given here as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Passengers can upgrade any time after reservation but at least 24 hours before their scheduled flight departure.</li>\r\n	<li>Economy class passengers (non-refundable flight tickets) do not have the option to upgrade or interchange from one class to another.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If a technical problem or airline error causes a flight delay, the airline offers passengers an alternate trip in a higher class than the one for which they have made a reservation. In such a case, the traveler was not required to pay any money to the airline.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Passenger members of the airline&#39;s membership program may upgrade their flight tickets without paying fees.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Qatar Airways Seat Upgrade Cost</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The seat upgrade cost depends upon the flight class in which the upgrade must be made. The time left for a scheduled departure, the flight class in which you proceed to upgrade, and the distance covered by the airlines also play an important role. However, the average upgrade cost with Qatar Airways will be from $4 to $100.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Where is the best place to sit on Qatar Airways?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The dubious seat configuration can be a lottery. Although Qatar&#39;s economy is typically 3-3-3, the front two rows of each section are 3-4-3, which means you hit jackpot with seats 25D and G (or the equivalent).</p>\r\n','We provide online help for how to select Qatar Airways economy classic seat so before selection find the seat selection policy then upgrade your flight seat and know about seat selection and upgrade flight seat cost.',NULL,'How To Get Free Seat Selection on Qatar Airways?','','Qatar Airways Seat Upgrade, Qatar Seat Selection Policy, Qatar Economy Classic Seat Selection ','seatSelection','2023-08-12','Active','','','','Qatar Economy Classic Seat Selection | Policy | Upgrade- Cost','qatar-economy-classic-seat-selection'),(42,NULL,'<h2><strong>How Do I Call Kenya Airways?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As indicated by the name, Kenya Airways is the flag carrier of Kenya and operates flights to over 50 destinations worldwide. The airline is acclaimed for offering some fantastic services to customers. It ensures their convenience before, during, and after the flight. If any customer faces any difficulty, it ensures they fix their issue on time. For this purpose, you must inform them of your inconvenience. You must now wonder how do I talk to a live person at Kenya Airways<strong><em>. </em></strong>The following article is enriched with complete information on Kenya Airways&#39; contact method. Kindly go through it carefully to understand it better.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Resolve Your Problem Over the Phone:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Calling customer service has been a basic method to get help in times of trouble or doubt. It enables you to directly have a word with a customer service representative and seek assistance. If you want to speak to an executive, call the Kenya Airways phone number<strong><em>, </em></strong>which is 1 (866) 536-9224. You will hear an IVR menu with multiple options. Listen to it carefully and select an appropriate option by pressing the correct key. You will soon connect with a representative, let them know your concern or query, and furnish them with your details. They will assist you optimally.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Create an inquiry with the airline:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Calls can get annoying at times due to long wait times. As a solution to this common problem, people prefer other methods to contact. One such method is to make an inquiry by filling out a form. The enlisted steps help you to get to the inquiry form.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Firstly, you have to open Kenya AIrways&rsquo; official website.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Click the &lsquo;Talk to Us&rsquo; option under the Guest Support tab.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Navigate through the next page and click the &lsquo;Enquiry&rsquo; option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A new form will automatically appear. Fill in the correct details in the form and recheck it before submitting.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, you should submit the form, and the customer service team will get back to you soon.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Seek Assistance via Email:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Writing an email is the next way that you can choose to inform your complaint or query to Kenya Airways. You can send an email to Kenya Airways Complaints Email<strong><em> </em></strong>address which is customer.relations@kenya-airways.com. Mention your details along with the issue you have faced, and the airline shall get back to you soon. Emails, however, do not provide an immediate response. You shall get a response from them in the next 24 to 48 hours</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Do I Contact Kenya Airways via Whatsapp?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nowadays, Kenya Airways is also available on WhatsApp. It addresses and resolves customer queries and complaints over WhatsApp. It saves time and provides quick responses. Now if you are thinking about how do I contact Kenya Airways via Whatsapp<strong><em>, </em></strong>take a sigh of relief as it is pretty simple to 