quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:529}\">Follow the Pre-Recorded call instructions and select the number as per your requirement.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:72,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:549}\">Press 0 to choose the preferred language.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:93,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:570}\">For bookings and timings of flight, press 2.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:114,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:591}\">Press 3 for cancellation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:135,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:612}\">For refund status and payment issues, press 4.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:156,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:633}\">Press 5 for a medical emergency.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:176,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:653}\">To register complaints, press 6.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:197,&quot;w&quot;:915,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:449,&quot;abs_y&quot;:674}\">If there are further issues, press * and talk to the live agent.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:231,&quot;w&quot;:995,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:409,&quot;abs_y&quot;:708}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:234,&quot;w&quot;:229,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:409,&quot;abs_y&quot;:711}\">Other Required details of the Airport:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:265,&quot;w&quot;:995,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:409,&quot;abs_y&quot;:742}\">Email Address:&nbsp;<a bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:110,&quot;y&quot;:268,&quot;w&quot;:89,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:499,&quot;abs_y&quot;:745}\" href=\"mailto:info@ocair.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@ocair.com</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:299,&quot;w&quot;:995,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:409,&quot;abs_y&quot;:776}\">Official Airport address: 18601 Airport Way, Santa Ana, CA 92707, United States</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How Do I Contact TSA SNA?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;If you are traveling from John Wayne Airport, also known as Santa Ana Airport, to know&nbsp;<strong>How do I contact TSA SNA?</strong>&nbsp;Please find the contact information below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TSA contact number:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;To get detailed information on TSA enrollment and related queries, please call on the phone number 855 347 8371 and speak to an authorized person.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operation hours of TSA number:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can contact on the above-mentioned TSA phone number:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday - Friday: 8.00 am to 10 pm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is the Santa Ana Airport Customer Service Number?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connect on the phone</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The airport customer service will give you complete information on the queries and confirm the assistance requests. You can call the number 949 252 5200 and inquire about the TSA and other services available at the airport.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Santa Ana Airport customer service hours:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can contact SNA airport customer service 24/7 for support and guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To know more about TSA at Santa Ana Airport and information on airport facilities, you can reach the customer service in the following ways:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Send an email:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;To get detailed information on queries, compose an email and send it to info@ocair.com, and John Wayne Airport customer service will revert to you within a short time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Submit a request to speak:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;In case you want to have a detailed discussion on the queries, please click on the link below to get a speaker from Santa Ana Airport customer service https://www.ocair.com/about/administration/community-outreach/request-speaker/</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Address of Santa Ana Airport:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can reach on the address of John Wayne Airport at Santa Ana to board the scheduled flight:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thomas F. Riley Terminal&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>18601 Airport Way</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Santa Ana, CA, 92707.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Airport Code:&nbsp;</strong>SNA</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Many Terminals are there at Santa Ana Airport?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Santa Ana Airport has 3 terminals: A, B, and C. Please call the Airport customer service to confirm the terminal of your scheduled flight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How early do you need to be at the SNA airport?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;To go through the check-in formalities at the airport and then complete the security check before boarding the flight, a passenger must reach the SNA Airport:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1- 2 hours prior to a domestic flight</li>\r\n	<li>3 hours prior to an international flight.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>And in case you need special assistance for differently abled persons, unmonitored minors, or senior citizens, please reach the airport early and inform the customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What Time Does SNA Airport Open?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>John Wayne Airport, or SNA Airport, is open 24/7 for flight arrivals and departures. Passengers can reach the airport anytime for their scheduled flights.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How long does it take to get through security at SNA?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;The security check time at SNA Airport can vary accordingly:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you have TSA Precheck: 15 - 20 minutes</li>\r\n	<li>If you go through the regular security check: Approx 30 minutes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How To Contact the Lost and Found of SNA Airport?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have misplaced an item at the SNA Airport, please report the issue to the airport police service on the phone number 949 252 5140 and get help to retrieve the lost item.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Facilities available at SNA Airport:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Information desks</li>\r\n	<li>Restaurants, cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Hotels</li>\r\n	<li>Waiting area with recliner chairs</li>\r\n	<li>Parking</li>\r\n	<li>Free pick and drop to the terminals</li>\r\n	<li>Luggage trolleys</li>\r\n	<li>Restrooms</li>\r\n	<li>Kids play zone</li>\r\n	<li>Pharmacy</li>\r\n	<li>Medical rooms</li>\r\n	<li>Banking services</li>\r\n	<li>ATM</li>\r\n	<li>Lounges</li>\r\n	<li>Several other services.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','If any traveler wants to get John Wayne Airport customer service so find here John Wayne Airport phone number and claim for lost and damage baggage at airport, airport open 24 hours.',NULL,'How Early Can You Get to John Wayne Airport?','','John Wayne Airport Baggage Claim, John Wayne Airport Flight Restrictions, ','article','2023-09-05','Active','','','','How Early Can You Get to John Wayne Airport | 24-Hours \\ Phone Number','how-early-can-you-get-to-john-wayne-airport'),(67,NULL,'<p>The visa of a state upholds a person&#39;s legal authenticity to enter into the boundary of a foreign state. When you have the urge to get into the United States, then you have to get a permission letter in the form of a visa. If you have queries such as What are the requirements to get a US visa? Then do not panic because the solution in reference to this has been defined at the bottom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Common Requirements for US Visa:- </strong>The visa of the United States of America has been classified into various categories as per class, and the requirements of documents could vary. But there are some requirements that could remain the same and the types of documents are as such:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Passport validity</li>\r\n	<li>Application form of Form DS-160</li>\r\n	<li>Visa application fee and payment process</li>\r\n	<li>Photo and fingerprint requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Proof of ties to home country</li>\r\n	<li>Required to find in the bank statement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>US visa application process:- </strong>When you are in possession of every required document then you can apply for a US visa. The ordinary visa application process has been defined at the bottom:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Head to the official website of the U.S., Bureau of Consular Affairs- travel.state.gov/content/travel.html</li>\r\n	<li>After that, fill out Form DS-160 from the home tab</li>\r\n	<li>There, you get to upload a photo too.</li>\r\n	<li>Then, pay a fee as per visa type after its approval</li>\r\n	<li>Later on, schedule an interview at your regional consulate office</li>\r\n	<li>Afterward, collect copies of every required data for preparing an interviews</li>\r\n	<li>If everything goes well then your visa could be issued.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Types of US Visas</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The legal documents needed to enter the United States depend on the purpose of entering its boundary. This is why one has to submit a relevant and appropriate document in accordance with that. Further, out of many, these are a few mostly highlighted visa categories such as Tourist, Work, and Student. Thus, you can get brief information about those visas from underneath.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Work visa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The permit to work in a foreign land is considered a work visa. This is an authorization letter issued by a country for a limited period of time till the period of them. However, this visa has been classified into multiple categories as per the working conditions. Thus, its names have been raised at the bottom:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>H-1b:- Person in Specialty Occupation</li>\r\n	<li>H-1b1:- Free Trade Agreement Professional</li>\r\n	<li>H-2a:- Temporary Agricultural Worker</li>\r\n	<li>H-2b:- Temporary Non-agricultural Worker</li>\r\n	<li>H-3:- Trainee or Special Education visitor</li>\r\n	<li>L: Intracompany Transferee</li>\r\n	<li>Individuals with Extraordinary Ability or Achievement</li>\r\n	<li>Artist or Entertainer</li>\r\n	<li>Artist or Entertainer&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Participant in an International Cultural Exchange Program</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tourist visa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you are willing to get in the United States for tourism purposes, then you get to secure a tourist visa from an embassy. This visa could not be used for conducting any kind of business activity on the land. You can have this for a short vacation, visiting with family or friends, and arranging medical treatment. Thus, the fee for getting this visa is around $180. Besides this, you can also apply for this visa for medical reasons and get into the United States.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Student visa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The United States of America enriches education facilities because of higher education systems with better colleges and universities. When you wish to get into one of those, then you could need a student visa in hand. This could be a permit to study till completion of the course and reach a paper. Moreover, the application made here is classified into F and M categories. Further, the details about those are as such:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Student visa F:-</strong> The student studying in a recognized university or college could be eligible to have this visa. Otherwise, a student studying in the English learning institutes.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exchange visa J:-</strong> This visa is allocated to students of exchange programs of high schools and universities.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Student visa M:-</strong> If you are traveling for an unacademic or vocational training purpose, then you could get this visa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Importance of selecting the right visa type</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When you wish to enter the United States on a passport of a foreign nation, then you have to get a visa for the same. Although there are numerous types of visas available in the US, selecting the correct one could be mandatory. Further, you can acknowledge the importance of getting the right one from the below:-&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You should be able to complete work properly without any interruption.</li>\r\n	<li>The support and perks from the states could also be shared.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You could escape from suffering any kind of monetary or other related document.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;You would not have to face any kind of legal obligations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Additional Documentation by Visa Type</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Whenever you could get to apply for a visa in the States, then you have to complete every required document on the basis types. Further, a description of those has been defined at the bottom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tourist visa:- </strong>When you have planned a vacation or have a medical emergency, then you can appeal for a tourist visa. Moreover, the tourist visa US requirements details of that have been shown at the bottom:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A valid passport to travel in the states</li>\r\n	<li>The visa application form, which is Form DS-160,</li>\r\n	<li>Invitation letters</li>\r\n	<li>Travel itinerary</li>\r\n	<li>Financial proof</li>\r\n	<li>Payment receipt of application fees</li>\r\n	<li>Printed photo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Work visa:- </strong>When you are willing to work in America, then you could have to apply for a work visa. In order to do that, you could have to fulfill work visa US requirements, and those are as such:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Form DS-160, work visa form&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A valid passport to enter in the United States</li>\r\n	<li>An application fees receipt of payment</li>\r\n	<li>Photo of applicant</li>\r\n	<li>Employment offer</li>\r\n	<li>Qualifications</li>\r\n	<li>Employer sponsorship letter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Student visa: </strong>The student willing to pursue their education over there has to carry a student visa. The applicant had to complete certain Student visa USA requirements to get those, and the information has been mentioned at the bottom:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Confirmation page of Form DS-160</li>\r\n	<li>A passport valid to enter the country</li>\r\n	<li>Fee receipt</li>\r\n	<li>Recent Photos</li>\r\n	<li>Certificate of Eligibility for Nonimmigrant (F-1)</li>\r\n	<li>Student Status- Academic and Language Students, Form I-20 or Certificate of Eligibility for Nonimmigrant (M-1)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Student Status for Vocational Students, Form I-20</li>\r\n	<li>Admission letter</li>\r\n	<li>Financial support</li>\r\n	<li>Intent to return</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h1><strong>What Documents are Required for a USA Visa?</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most important elements for entering into a nation is a visa. But if your nation had a friendly relationship then you may not need those. When you don&#39;t have such leverage then the visa needs to be applied with the appropriate document. Hence, the list of all documents for the U.S. visa requirements is as such:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Completion of Form DS-160</li>\r\n	<li>Updates photos</li>\r\n	<li>Sufficient funds in the bank statement</li>\r\n	<li>Application fees receipts</li>\r\n	<li>Passport with a validity to enter in region</li>\r\n	<li>Purpose of trip</li>\r\n	<li>Intend to get into the nation</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to bear the cost of a trip.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How Much Bank Statement is Required for a USA Visa?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The visa applicant from the United States has to gather ample documents to complete the procedure and reflecting a bank statement is one of them. The minimum balance needed in a bank could be depended on the visa form. However, the common amounts that are needed in a bank are from $6000 to $11000. If you need accurate information then you can search on the official web page or get to the consulate office of your region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What Documents Should I bring to my U.S. Visa Interview?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The initial stage for applying for a visa in the United States is completing a Form DS-160. If it gets approved then you have to pay application fees of around $185 and schedule an interview. However, the age group younger than 14 and older than 80 years could not be required to schedule an interview. Further, the age of 14 to 79 years is needed to schedule an interview with an appropriate document. Moreover, all the documents required for US visa interview are listed at the bottom points:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Copy of Form Form DS-160</li>\r\n	<li>Valid passport</li>\r\n	<li>Photo&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bank statement copies</li>\r\n	<li>Document showing the purpose of visit to destinations</li>\r\n	<li>Intent to depart after departing</li>\r\n	<li>Eligible to pay the cost of the entire trip</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is the Easiest Way to Get a US Visa?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When you have sufficient documents for getting a visa to the United States, then you get to apply the same. In order to do that, you get a different mode, and the easiest process for this is online. There you fill out a form and also gain the required document information. If you need a hint for that then act along the steps that have been mentioned at the bottom:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get to the authenticated page of the Bureau of Consular Affairs of the U.S.- travel.state.gov/content/travel.html</li>\r\n	<li>There, fill out a form and attach an updated photo</li>\r\n	<li>Later on, pay an application fee that could be around $185.</li>\r\n	<li>After that, schedule an interview (if you are in an age group of 14 to 79 years)</li>\r\n	<li>Progress all the documents stated in the form and get to the center</li>\r\n	<li>When everything could be appropriate, your application could be approved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How Much Money Do You Need for a US Visa?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The U.S. visa also relies on the bank balance. So, to have that, you may have to put that amount in your bank statement, which is around $6000 to $11000. Besides this, you would also have to pay $185 as an application fee after approval of the application. Furthermore, the fee is not static and could be changed at any moment. So, you can get to the consulate office for confirmation or check its official web page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is a Good Reason to Get a US Visa?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The visa of a nation is not just a legal permit to enter its boundary, but it shows and shares the culture of that country. So when you are determined to get into the United States then a visa is an important part of the journey. However, the adequate and appropriate reason to have a visa has been demonstrated at the bottom points:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You could be a legal entity of a nation and could be governed accordingly.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Able to make freely within your visa limit area without any disruption</li>\r\n	<li>Conduct a task and also be able to receive growth legally.</li>\r\n	<li>Can access most of the rights and duties prescribed in a constitution</li>\r\n	<li>To make the purpose of the visit more delightful and cozy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Final word</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The visa application in the United States of America includes a number of elements that might create a complication of thought. But this would not happen now because a solution for a query such as&nbsp;the documents required for a U.S. visa<strong>, </strong>has been presented above heading. Still, following these conditions, it might not be necessary then you can get an approved visa. Besides this, you can also visit your nearby embassy and have an answer head-to-head.</p>\r\n','To obtain a US visa, you\'ll need to follow a few essential steps. First, determine the visa type that suits your purpose (tourism, work, study, etc.). Complete the DS-160 form online, pay the application fee, and schedule an interview at the nearest US embassy or consulate. ',NULL,'What are the Requirements to Get a US Visa?','','What are the requirements to get a US visa?, Common Requirements for a US Visa, Visa application fee and payment process, Types of US Visas, Importance of selecting the right visa type, Additional Documentation by Visa Type, What all documents are required for a USA visa?, How much bank statement is required for USA visa?, What documents should I bring to my U.S. visa interview?, What is the easiest way to get US visa?, How much money do you need for a US visa?, What is a good reason to get a US visa?','visaCard','2023-09-05','Active','','','','US Visa Requirements: A Comprehensive Guide','what-are-the-requirements-to-get-a-us-visa'),(68,NULL,'<p>Un grupo significa un n&uacute;mero de personas que viajan al mismo destino como familia o desde una organizaci&oacute;n. Puede ser unas grandes vacaciones familias o un grupo de viaje o estudiantes de vacaciones. El n&uacute;mero de personas debe ser superior a 10 y solo, entonces, se considera viaje en grupo. Si los pasajeros no tienen idea sobre&nbsp;&iquest;C&oacute;mo hacer una reserva de grupo en Vueling?,&nbsp;no hay problema. Hay tres maneras para los pasajeros para hacer una reserva, pueden reservarlo v&iacute;a en-linea, via telefono, o pueden ir al aeropuerto para hacer una reserva de grupo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-El proceso de En-l&iacute;nea.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Los pasajeros necesitan rellenar el formulario de viajes grupales en-l&iacute;nea. El proceso para hacer una reserva de grupo en-l&iacute;nea es muy sencillo. Pueden seguir todos&nbsp; los puntos que menciona debajo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Van a ir al sitio web oficial de Vueling Airline.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Clican en la opci&oacute;n de &ldquo;viaje en grupo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Entonces, deben hacer clic en la pesta&ntilde;a de &ldquo;reserva de grupo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-En la p&aacute;gina siguiente, proporciona los detalles, como, el responsable del grupo tiene informaci&oacute;n de contacto, nombre del grupo, n&uacute;meros de pasajeros en el grupo, detalles del pasaporte si viaja internacionalmente.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Siguiente, pueden enviar la solicitud necesaria.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Y, una vez que hayan completado el proceso, pagar&aacute;n el pago de reserva de grupos.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-A Traves del Telefono&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Para hacer una reserva de grupo, los pasajeros pueden conectarse con el ejecutivo de la aerol&iacute;nea, marcando el n&uacute;mero de&nbsp;Tel&eacute;fono Vueling Grupos,&nbsp;900645000. Pueden obtener una asistencia tan pronto como sea posible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; es el Grupo 1 2 3 Vueling?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>-Grupo de Embarque 1 incluida la clase negocio, Socios ejecutivos club Gold socios y one World Emerald Members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Grupo de Embarque 2 incluida miembros silver del ejecutivo club de corta distancia y miembros de oneworld Sapphire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Grupo de Embarque 3 incluida miembros Bounce del ejecutivo Club de Corta distancia y miembros de oneworld Ruby.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; son las Condiciones de Grupos Vueling?&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Para hacer reserva de grupo, los pasajeros necesitan conocer sobre las condiciones de Grupos Vueling que menciona a continuaci&oacute;n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-El periodo de validez de la cotizaci&oacute;n depende de la fecha de solicitud del grupo y est&aacute; sujeto a disponibilidad de asientos en la clase ofertada en la fecha de aceptaci&oacute;n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Las reservas de grupo deber&aacute;n solicitarse y aceptarse al menos setenta y dos horas antes de la salida del vuelo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Una vez aceptada la cotizaci&oacute;n a trav&eacute;s de la plataforma de grupos, entonces, el 20% del monto total deber&aacute; ser pagado dentro de los cinco d&iacute;as calendario siguientes a la aceptaci&oacute;n de la cotizaci&oacute;n. Y el 80% restante del importe total deber&aacute; abonarse hasta 35 d&iacute;as antes de la salida del primer vuelo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Vueling &uacute;nicamente se pondr&aacute; en contacto con el solicitante del grupo, identificado en el proceso de reserva, como, &ldquo;Datos del solicitante del presupuesto&rdquo;, a quien se le enviar&aacute; toda la informaci&oacute;n con relaci&oacute;n de la reserva.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; son los grupos de embarque Vueling?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Cuando los pasajeros est&eacute;n viajando con Vueling Airlines, pueden notar que su billete tiene impreso un n&uacute;mero de grupo de embarque. Este n&uacute;mero del 1 al 5, es la prioridad seg&uacute;n la cual se le pedir&aacute; que suba el avi&oacute;n. Generalmente, el grupo de embarque 1 va primero y 5 va &uacute;ltimo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','Si alguien busca una reserva de grupo en Vueling, busque el proceso y conozca cuál es el precio y las condiciones de la reserva de grupo 1 2 3 en las aerolíneas Vueling.',NULL,'Cómo Hacer Una Reserva de Grupo en Vueling?','','Cómo Hacer Una Reserva de Grupo en Vueling | 1 2 3 Reserva de Grupo','articleES','2023-09-07','Active','','','','Cómo Hacer Una Reserva de Grupo en Vueling | 1 2 3 Reserva de Grupo','como-hacer-una-reserva-de-grupo-en-vueling'),(69,NULL,'<p>Si desea viajar con Jetblue Airline, pero tiene problemas para encontrar el mejor vuelo, puede ponerse en contacto con un experto en atenci&oacute;n al cliente para resolver todos sus problemas. Hay muchas opciones disponibles para ponerse en contacto como llamar, chat en vivo, correo electr&oacute;nico, medios de comunicaci&oacute;n social, oficina de billetes y otros. Si no tienes ni idea sobre&nbsp;&iquest;C&oacute;mo me puedo comunicar con JetBlue en espa&nti